// 765432.bps — Polyrhythmic piece for Cronos dance production
// Traduit de bp3-engine/library/experimental/765432/grammar.gr
//
// Composed by Andrine Bel for the Cronos dance production (1994).
// Performed by Suresh, Smriti, Olivier, Vijayshree, Arindam, Andreine.
// A polyrhythmic piece using undetermined silences (...)
// Glossaries had not yet been implemented when this grammar was designed.
// The last subgrammar could be replaced with "-gl.D50"

@core
@controls
@alphabet.western:midi

// --- Sous-grammaire 1 [mode:ord] ---

S -> Internal C47 Part1 Canon C46[vel:90] Part2 [mode:ord]
Part1 -> {Suresh1,... Smriti1,... Olivier1,... Vijayshree1,... Arindam1,... Andreine1}
Part2 -> {Suresh2,Smriti2 ...,Olivier2 ...,Vijayshree2 ...,Arindam2 ...,Andreine2 ...}

-----

// --- Sous-grammaire 2 [mode:ord] ---

Suresh1 -> SuMov7x7 SuSil7x7 SuMov6x7 SuSil6x7 SuMov5x7 SuSil5x7 SuMov4x7 SuSil4x7 SuMov3x7 SuSil3x7 SuMov2x7 SuSil2x7 SuMov1x7 SuSil1x7 [mode:ord]
Smriti1 -> SmMov6x6 SmSil6x6 SmMov5x6 SmSil5x6 SmMov4x6 SmSil4x6 SmMov3x6 SmSil3x6 SmMov2x6 SmSil2x6 SmMov1x6 SmSil1x6
Olivier1 -> OlMov5x5 OlSil5x5 OlMov4x5 OlSil4x5 OlMov3x5 OlSil3x5 OlMov2x5 OlSil2x5 OlMov1x5 OlSil1x5
Vijayshree1 -> ViMov4x4 ViSil4x4 ViMov3x4 ViSil3x4 ViMov2x4 ViSil2x4 ViMov1x4 ViSil1x4
Arindam1 -> ArMov3x3 ArSil3x3 ArMov2x3 ArSil2x3 ArMov1x3 ArSil1x3
Andreine1 -> AnMov2x2 AnSil2x2 AnMov1x2 AnSil1x2

-----

// --- Sous-grammaire 3 [mode:ord] ---

Suresh2 -> SuMov7x7 SuMov6x6 SuMov5x5 SuMov4x4 SuMov3x3 SuMov2x2 SuMov1x1 [mode:ord]
Smriti2 -> SmMov6x6 SmMov5x5 SmMov4x4 SmMov3x3 SmMov2x2 SmMov1x1
Olivier2 -> OlMov5x5 OlMov4x4 OlMov3x3 OlMov2x2 OlMov1x1
Vijayshree2 -> ViMov4x4 ViMov3x3 ViMov2x2 ViMov1x1
Arindam2 -> ArMov3x3 ArMov2x2 ArMov1x1
Andreine2 -> AnMov2x2 AnMov1x1

-----

// --- Sous-grammaire 4 [mode:ord] — Suresh cycles x7 and descending ---

SuMov1x7 -> SuCycle7 [mode:ord]
SuSil1x7 -> SuMov1x7
SuMov2x7 -> SuCycle7 SuCycle7
SuSil2x7 -> SuMov2x7
SuMov3x7 -> SuCycle7 SuCycle7 SuCycle7
SuSil3x7 -> SuMov3x7
SuMov4x7 -> SuCycle7 SuCycle7 SuCycle7 SuCycle7
