SuMov5x7 -> SuCycle7 SuCycle7 SuCycle7 SuCycle7 SuCycle7
SuSil5x7 -> SuMov5x7
SuMov6x7 -> SuCycle7 SuCycle7 SuCycle7 SuCycle7 SuCycle7 SuCycle7
SuSil6x7 -> SuMov6x7
SuMov7x7 -> SuCycle7 SuCycle7 SuCycle7 SuCycle7 SuCycle7 SuCycle7 SuCycle7
SuSil7x7 -> SuMov7x7

SuMov1x1 -> SuCycle1
SuSil1x1 -> SuMov1x1
SuMov2x2 -> SuCycle2 SuCycle2
SuSil2x2 -> SuMov2x2
SuMov3x3 -> SuCycle3 SuCycle3 SuCycle3
SuSil3x3 -> SuMov3x3
SuMov4x4 -> SuCycle4 SuCycle4 SuCycle4 SuCycle4
SuSil4x4 -> SuMov4x4
SuMov5x5 -> SuCycle5 SuCycle5 SuCycle5 SuCycle5 SuCycle5
SuSil5x5 -> SuMov5x5
SuMov6x6 -> SuCycle6 SuCycle6 SuCycle6 SuCycle6 SuCycle6 SuCycle6
SuSil6x6 -> SuMov6x6

-----

// --- Sous-grammaire 5 [mode:ord] — Smriti cycles ---

SmMov1x6 -> SmCycle6 [mode:ord]
SmSil1x6 -> SmMov1x6
SmMov2x6 -> SmCycle6 SmCycle6
SmSil2x6 -> SmMov2x6
SmMov3x6 -> SmCycle6 SmCycle6 SmCycle6
SmSil3x6 -> SmMov3x6
SmMov4x6 -> SmCycle6 SmCycle6 SmCycle6 SmCycle6
SmSil4x6 -> SmMov4x6
