SmSil5x6 -> SmMov5x6
SmMov6x6 -> SmCycle6 SmCycle6 SmCycle6 SmCycle6 SmCycle6 SmCycle6
SmSil6x6 -> SmMov6x6

SmMov1x1 -> SmCycle1
SmSil1x1 -> SmMov1x1
SmMov2x2 -> SmCycle2 SmCycle2
