// --- Sous-grammaire 6 [mode:ord] — Olivier cycles ---

OlMov1x5 -> OlCycle5 [mode:ord]
OlSil1x5 -> OlMov1x5
OlMov2x5 -> OlCycle5 OlCycle5
OlSil2x5 -> OlMov2x5
OlMov3x5 -> OlCycle5 OlCycle5 OlCycle5
OlSil3x5 -> OlMov3x5
