OlSil4x5 -> OlMov4x5
OlMov5x5 -> OlCycle5 OlCycle5 OlCycle5 OlCycle5 OlCycle5
OlSil5x5 -> OlMov5x5

OlMov1x1 -> OlCycle1
OlSil1x1 -> OlMov1x1
