// --- Sous-grammaire 7 [mode:ord] — Vijayshree cycles ---

ViMov1x4 -> ViCycle4 [mode:ord]
ViSil1x4 -> ViMov1x4
ViMov2x4 -> ViCycle4 ViCycle4
ViSil2x4 -> ViMov2x4
ViMov3x4 -> ViCycle4 ViCycle4 ViCycle4
ViSil3x4 -> ViMov3x4
ViMov4x4 -> ViCycle4 ViCycle4 ViCycle4 ViCycle4
ViSil4x4 -> ViMov4x4

ViMov1x1 -> ViCycle1
ViSil1x1 -> ViMov1x1
ViMov2x2 -> ViCycle2 ViCycle2
ViSil2x2 -> ViMov2x2
ViMov3x3 -> ViCycle3 ViCycle3 ViCycle3
