// --- Sous-grammaire 9 [mode:ord] — Andreine cycles ---

AnMov1x2 -> AnCycle2 [mode:ord]
AnSil1x2 -> AnMov1x2
AnMov2x2 -> AnCycle2 AnCycle2
AnSil2x2 -> AnMov2x2

AnMov1x1 -> AnCycle1
AnSil1x1 -> AnMov1x1

-----

// --- Sous-grammaire 10 [mode:ord] — Canon ---

Canon -> Twist Walk Stretch Bend Jump Turn [mode:ord]
Twist -> Sm Tik Tik Tik Tik Tik Su Tik Tik Tik Tik Ol Tik Tik Tik Ar Tik Tik Vi Tik An
Walk -> Sm Su Tik Ol Tik Tik Ar Tik Tik Tik Vi Tik Tik Tik Tik An Tik Tik Tik Tik Tik
Stretch -> Twist
Bend -> Walk
Jump -> Twist
Turn -> Walk

-----

// --- Sous-grammaire 11 [mode:sub1] — Cycle definitions ---

SuCycle7 -> Su Tik Tik Tik Tik Tik Tik [mode:sub1]
SuCycle6 -> Su Tik Tik Tik Tik Tik
SuCycle5 -> Su Tik Tik Tik Tik
SuCycle4 -> Su Tik Tik Tik
SuCycle3 -> Su Tik Tik
SuCycle2 -> Su Tik
SuCycle1 -> Su
SmCycle6 -> Sm - - - - -
SmCycle5 -> Sm - - - -
SmCycle4 -> Sm - - -
SmCycle3 -> Sm - -
SmCycle2 -> Sm -
SmCycle1 -> Sm
OlCycle5 -> Ol - - - -
OlCycle4 -> Ol - - -
OlCycle3 -> Ol - -
OlCycle2 -> Ol -
OlCycle1 -> Ol
ViCycle4 -> Vi - - -
ViCycle3 -> Vi - -
ViCycle2 -> Vi -
ViCycle1 -> Vi
ArCycle3 -> Ar - -
ArCycle2 -> Ar -
ArCycle1 -> Ar
AnCycle2 -> An -
AnCycle1 -> An

-----

// --- Sous-grammaire 12 [mode:sub1] — Notes (simultaneous with 1) ---

Su -> {1,do4-} [mode:sub1]
Sm -> {1,mi4-}
Ol -> {1,sol4-}
Vi -> {1,do5-}
Ar -> {1,mi5-}
An -> {1,sol5-}

Tik -> {1,do7-}

-----

// --- Sous-grammaire 13 [mode:ord] — D-50 MIDI setup ---

Internal -> script(MIDI program 1) script(MIDI controller #98 = 0 channel 1) [mode:ord]
C46 -> script(MIDI program 94)
C47 -> script(MIDI program 95)
PedalOn -> switchon(64,1)
PedalOff -> switchoff(64,1)
